A short documentary split into 6 chapters
Run time:- 00:22:01

In the latest Discovering.... documentary, leading music journalists look back at the enduring music of Dire Straits.
Led by Mark Knopfler, the band recorded six studio albums, including the bestselling Brothers in Arms.
We find out how the US were more receptive to their sound, whilst the UK audience needed more convincing as the punk movement was taking hold
